              </p>

              <div class="mcp-troubleshooting">
                <details class="mcp-troubleshooting__item">
                  <summary class="mcp-troubleshooting__problem">
                    <i class="bi bi-exclamation-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    Connection refused on localhost:8080
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down mcp-troubleshooting__chevron" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                  </summary>
                  <div class="mcp-troubleshooting__solution">
                    <p>Ensure LichtFeld Studio is running and MCP is enabled in Preferences. Check that the port isn't blocked by a firewall.</p>
                  </div>
                </details>
                <details class="mcp-troubleshooting__item">
                  <summary class="mcp-troubleshooting__problem">
                    <i class="bi bi-exclamation-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    Tools execute but return 404
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down mcp-troubleshooting__chevron" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                  </summary>
                  <div class="mcp-troubleshooting__solution">
                    <p>Verify the tool name matches exactly (case-sensitive). Check /mcp/manifest for available tools.</p>
                  </div>
                </details>
                <details class="mcp-troubleshooting__item">
                  <summary class="mcp-troubleshooting__problem">
                    <i class="bi bi-exclamation-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    Camera animations stutter or fail
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down mcp-troubleshooting__chevron" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                  </summary>
                  <div class="mcp-troubleshooting__solution">
                    <p>Reduce keyframe complexity or increase animation duration. Ensure scene is fully loaded before animating.</p>
                  </div>
                </details>
                <details class="mcp-troubleshooting__item">
                  <summary class="mcp-troubleshooting__problem">
                    <i class="bi bi-exclamation-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    Training status not updating in real-time
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down mcp-troubleshooting__chevron" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                  </summary>
                  <div class="mcp-troubleshooting__solution">
                    <p>Connect to the SSE endpoint at /mcp/sse for live updates, or poll /mcp/resources/training/status.</p>
                  </div>
                </details>
                <details class="mcp-troubleshooting__item">
                  <summary class="mcp-troubleshooting__problem">
                    <i class="bi bi-exclamation-circle" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    Python client can't connect
                    <i class="bi bi-chevron-down mcp-troubleshooting__chevron" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                  </summary>
                  <div class="mcp-troubleshooting__solution">
                    <p>Verify the mcp Python package is installed: pip install mcp. Check that the server_url matches LichtFeld Studio's MCP port.</p>
                  </div>
                </details>
